data.description:
Ground level condo located in North Reston directly behind North Point Plaza. 2 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, 1 additional sink outside of the bathroom. Custom makeup vanity with quartz countertop. Brand new Samsung washer and dryer. Wood burning fireplace. Sliding glass doors to outdoor patio and storage area. 1 assigned parking spot and lots of additional parking nearby. Short walk to North Point Plaza and Lake Newport Pool. 5 min drive to Reston Town Center. 10 min drive to the metro. Pets allowed. Available Jan 1!

Owner pays HOA, water 
Tenant pays electric and cable/wifi 
1 year lease minimum
